patthana17.29:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ vipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho navipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
patthana17.29:1.1_1: adhipatiyā cha …pe… aññamaññe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana17.29:2.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
patthana17.29:3.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
